        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">刚开始 初始化 一个 目录的时候</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"> （注意编写文件的时候  选择  其他编辑工具  ue 或者 notepaid 格式选择utf-8）</span><br><span class="line">然后</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> d:/github</span><br><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">创建一个叫做  readme.txt 的文件</span><br><span class="line">git add 把文件添加到本地git库  （先进行 add）</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">"wrote a readme file"</span> (然后进行commit)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight sh"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">可以同时add  多个  然后一次性 commit</span><br><span class="line">然后  修改  一个 readme.txt 文件</span><br><span class="line">git status</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git diff</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git add</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git status</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><blockquote><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/r8l8q8/article/details/80015330" target="_blank" rel="noopener">https://blog.csdn.net/r8l8q8/article/details/80015330</a></p></blockquote>]]></content>
      
      
      
